  Thau ni chiN5 e5 tai7-chi3, A-eng tau5 hou7 Jit8-seng thiaN, Jit8-seng kong2 khai-hak8 liau2 chiah theh8 nng7-chheng-khou hou7--i. ¡§Thai3 e7 khai chiah siong?¡¨ Jit8-seng chiaN5 m7-sin3: ¡§Si7 m7-si7 kau ho2-giah8-lang5-kiaN2, soah pian3 phaN3 khai--khi3?¡¨ M7-chai si7 a-kong thiaN3 sun, tui3 A-koan hoan2-siong5 e5 tai7-chi3 ia7 bo5 ti3-i3. A-eng thiaN in ta-koaN iau2 theh8 chiN5 hou7 A-koan, sim-lai7 siuN7 chit-e5 gin2-a2 si7 teh an2-choaN2 khai: ¡§A-pa, i2-au7 m7-thang theh8 hou7--i, siuN gau5 khai--a-lah.¡¨ Sui-jian5 Jit8-seng kong2-tioh8 leng5 kau leng5, hong7 kau hong7, un2-ku--e5 kau tong3-gong7, pi2 teng2 pi2 e7 pi2 boe7 liau2. Chong2--si7 kap ho2-giah8-lang5-kiaN2 cho3-hoe2, sit8-chai7 bo5 hit-e5 seN3-mia7 thang hiah phaN3 khai--lah. Kheng3-tong5 khoaN3-hoat to7 bo5-kang5--louh, ¡§Ai3 chu3-i3 A-koan thak8-chheh, kau-iu2 e5 cheng5-heng5, siong7 tiong7-iau3 ha7-kho3 liau2-au7 teh chhong3 siaN2.¡¨ A-koan gau5 khai, lian5 kam2-a2-tiam3 e5 chiN5 to ni, hou7 Kheng3-tong5 kam2-kak tai7-chi3 bo5 tan-sun5: ¡§Tioh8 chha5 khoaN3-mai7--leh chiah ho2.¡¨ ¡§Beh an2-choaN2 chha5?¡¨ A-eng chiaN5 hoan5-lo2: ¡§Li2 ma7 the3 goa2 siuN7 khoaN3-mai7--leh. KaN2 m7-thang hou7 lang5 thoa phaiN2--khi3 to7 hai7--louh.¡¨
  A-eng tui3 A-koan ti7 Tai5-tiong e5 seng-oah8 khi2-ki long2 bo5 liau2-kai2, chit-ma2 thiaN Kheng3-tong5 kong2 gau5 khai kah e7 thau ni chiN5, kiaN pian3 phaiN2--khi3. Tu2 teh siuN7 kah bo5 phiat-pou7, Kheng3-tong5 kong2 Chhai2-giok8 bat the5-khi2 in tong5-oh8 e5 a-chi2 kap A-koan kang7-pan, e7-sai2 thau3-koe3 koan-he7 lai5 chha5 mng7 A-koan thak8-chheh e5 cheng5-heng5. SiaN2 chai, chit8-e7 mng7 loh8-khi3 kau3 te3, A-koan thak8-chheh tuh-ku, kau put-sam put-su3 e5 lam5-peng5-iu2, am3-si5 tiaN7-tiaN7 kou3 sng2 tian7-oan5 e5 tai7-chi3, chit8-hang7 chit8-hang7 lau7-siap--chhut-lai5. M7-na7 A-eng, lian5 Kheng3-tong5 to khi3 hou7 kiaN chit8-tio5, m7 siong-sin3 A-koan e7 pian3 kah an2-ne. ¡§Chit-e5 gin2-a2 bo5 ho2-ho2-a2 ka3, u7-iaN2 e7 bai2, u7-iaN2 e7 bai2.....¡¨ Sui-jian5 A-eng khi3 kah lak8-lak8-chhoah, m7-koh, to bo5 joa7 ku2, A-eng tau5 Khegn3-tong5 kong2: ¡§....Goa2 to iau2-boe7 khui-chhui3 ka7 me7--leh, i to7 kong2 goa2 cho3 ma-ma choan thiaN pat8-lang5 e5 peh8-chhat8-oe7, sin3 ka-ti7 cha-bou2-kian2 boe7 koe3.¡¨ A-eng it-tit8 io5-thau5: ¡§Iau2 me7 goa2 toa7-kiaN sio2-koai3, kap cha-pou gin2-a2 chhit-tho5, sng2 chit8-e7 tian7-oan5, na2 kho3-goa7 oah8-tang7--leh, u7 siaN2 tai7-put-liau2!¡¨ Soah na2-chhiuN7 liah8 boe7 tiaN7: ¡§Kam2 e7 lan2 siuN kou2-pan2, toe3 si5-se3 boe7 tioh8? Ah iah-si7 ka7 gin2-a2 siuN7 tui3 bai2 khi3?¡¨ ThiaN A-eng kong2-tioh8 oe7 peng2-lai5 peng2-khi3.
  ¡§An2-ne--lah, li2 tui3 hak8-hau7 lau7-su khi3 chim-chiok, am3-si5-a2 goa2 poah-kang lai5 chha5 khoaN3 u7-iaN2 kou3 sng2--bo5?¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 an-ui3 A-eng: ¡§Bo5 tiaN7-tioh8 lan2 ka7 khoaN3 phian--khi3 iah8 bo5 it-teng7.¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 chiam-tui3 A-koan cho3-hoe2 hia chhit-tho5 peng5-iu2 tiok8-chhiu2. Thau5-a2 iau2 ioh si7 tong5-oh8--leh, chit8-e7 ka7 liau2-kai2, hun7-chu2 hok8-chap, u7 to5-hak8 e5 hak8-seng, loa7-loa7-so5 e5 chhit-tho5-gin2-a2. Chit-tin7 lang5 kong2 si7 peng5-iu2, put-ju5 kong2 ai3 chiah8, heng3 sng2 hap8 oa2--lai5-e5. I2 tian7-tong7 iu5-lok8-tiuN5 ui5 tiong-sim, sng2-tioh8 kui-am3 m7-chai thiam2. Che thai3 si7 teh thak8-chheh, kin-pun2 si7 leh chhit-tho5! Leng7-goa7 A-koan in lau7-su ma7 kong2 i put-si5 teh chheng2-ka3 hioh-khun3. ¡§An2-ne beh an2-choaN2? Chit8-e5 gin2-a2 nah e7 chiah hong3-tong7!¡¨ A-eng khi3 koh kip, m7 hou7 toa3 Tai5-tiong, beh ah A-koan poaN tng2-lai5 thong-hak8. A-koan si2 to m7 poaN tng2--lai5, A-eng chiN5 tong3 he7--leh m7 hou7--i, siuN7 beh pek i tng2--lai5. Kheng3-tong5 kin2 chah8--leh, kong2 tian-to3 e7 khi3 hai7 i. U7-iaN2 A-koan chhiang3-siaN tng2--lai5, kong2 na7 bo5 kia3 seng-oah8-hui3 khi3, beh khi3 iu5-lok8-tiuN5 cho3¡y¤p©f¡z.... Tng teh siuN7 bo5, beh an2-choaN2 choaiN7 A-koan kiaN5 tng2-lai5 chiaN3-lou7....
  Kheng3-tong5 koh chha5 chhut chhit-tho5 hit-chun7, u7 sin be2 ki-chhia to7 khia5 jip8-khi3 tng3-tiam3--e5; u7 thau khan pat8-lang5 ki-chhia--e5; u7 ka7 hak8-seng kha3-iu5--e5; u7 suh kiong5-lek8-ka, chiah8 be5-hoan3-ioh8, koh u7 be7 ang5-tiong, peh8-pan2--e5.... Siong7 kiaN-hiaN5 si7 ti7 A-koan chheh-thoah-a2 hoat-hian7 tioh8 nng7-liap8 ioh8-oan5-a2! Goan5-lai5 A-eng thiaN Kheng3-tong5 e5 oe7, toa3 sou2-hui3 khi3 Tai5-tiong, sun7-soa3 khng3 A-koan tng2--lai5. SiaN2-lang5 chai A-koan long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lang5, lian5 hak8-hau7 to bo5 khi3, A-eng chiN5 khe3 chheh-thoah-a2 si5 chhiau-tioh8 hit nng7-liap8 ioh8-a2--e5. Kui2--lo7 kang lai5, ui7-tioh8 A-koan, Kheng3-tong5 chhai3-hng5-a2 bo5-eng5 soah, to7 khia5 ki-chhia khi3 Tai5-tiong, keh thiN-kng chiah tng2--lai5. Mng7 an2-choaN2 chha5--e5, chhio3-chhio3-a2 in3 i chhit-tho5-te2 chhut-sin, chu7-iu2 in e5 chhit-tho5-a2-pou7. A-eng bo5-i3-tiong chhiau-tioh8 nng7-liap8 ioh8-oan5-a2, siuN7-khi2 Kheng3-tong5 chit kui2 kang teh kong2, siau3-lian5 gin2-a2 chiah8 be5-hoan3-ioh8 e5 tai7-chi3.... Ui7-tioh8 kiaN kap Kheng3-tong5 sio chhut-lou7, ia7 bo5 tan2 A-koan, si7 kin2 koaN2 tng2-lai5 chhai3-hng5-a2 theh8 hou7 kam3-teng7. Kheng3-tong5 chhai3 tu2 khau ho2, moh ti7 kau--nih thoa7-chui2. ThiaN A-eng kong2 chhiau-tioh8 ioh8-oan5-a2, chhai3 kin2 thoa7-thoa7--leh, moh khi2-lai5 hoaN7-teng2, ki3-chai7 chui2 lam5 kah kui-nia2 khou3. ¡§Ah! Kau5-kiaN5--a, chit8-liap8 si7 peh8-pan2, chit8-liap8 si7 po2-che3-oan5 pau an-hui-tha-beng7 neh.¡¨
  Kheng3-tong5 lioh--chit8-e7 hoah chin hiong5-kong5: ¡§Chhoan3 kiaN chhoan3 tioh8!¡¨ Chhai3 khng3--loh8 chhut-chhiu2 tui3 ka-ti7 au7-nau2 phah--loh8-khi3: ¡§Kai si2--a, hou7 lang5 khan khi3 chiah8 tok8--a-lah,¡¨ ¡§An2-ne si7 beh an2-choaN2?¡¨ A-eng hou7 hoah-tioh8 khi2 tioh8-kiaN: ¡§I si2 to m7 tng2--lai5, si7 beh an2-choaN2?¡¨ ¡§Liah8 ma7 ai3 liah8 tng2--lai5,¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 kong2-tioh8 cham2-teng-chiat8-thih: ¡§Bo5, ah to ai3 ah tng2--lai5!¡¨ ¡§M7-koh, m7-koh..., he ioh8-a2 kam2 hiah li7-hai7?¡¨ ¡§Li2 ka7 siuN7 kap ma2-hui kang7-khoan2 to7 bo5 m7-tioh8. Bo5 chiah8 e7 gian3, ju2 chiah8 ju2 si2!¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 khoaN3 A-eng tiam7-tiam7, ioh si7 m7-chai khin-tang7: ¡§Li2 siuN7, ui7-tioh8 chong5 chiN5 teh gian3, siaN2 tai7-chi3 cho3 boe7--chhut-lai5? Thau ni chiN5, hau-siau5-oe7 chit8 toa7-tui..., chhut-thau5 e7 ju2 lai5 ju2 che7 oh.¡¨ Chit8-e7 khoaN3 A-eng teh thi5-thu5, chin the3 chhau-sim: ¡§Na7 bo5 kin2 chhoa7 tng2-lai5 kai2-tiau7, kui-boe2 kui-e5-lang5 e7 khioh-kak--lah.¡¨ ¡§...chhoa7 si7 ai3 kin2 chhoa7--tng2-lai5, m7-koh A-koan seng3-te7 hiah jiat8, nge7 ah tng2--lai5, tu2 kap i tiN5 boe7 soah.¡¨ ¡§Chit si5-chun7 boe7-tang3 hou7 hoaN-hi2 kam-goan7--louh. Chit8-e5 chiah8 tok8 e5 lang5, i kui-khou-lang5 long2 hou7 tok8-phin2 khong3-che3--khi3. Chit8-jit8 kau3 am3 long2 si7 teh chong5 chiN5 be2 tok8 teh gian3, na7 khi3 tng7 cham7, he pi2 si2 to khah kan-khou2. Ui7-tioh8 koe3-gian3, siaN2 tai7-chi3 to cho3 e7 chhut--lai5! A-eng, li2 chai--bo5? Ui7-tioh8 teh gian3, li2 kio3 i chhong3 siaN2, i long2 in2--li2.....¡¨
  Chu7 cho3-hoe2 i2-lai5, A-eng m7-bat thiaN Kheng3-tong5 kong2 hiah che7 oe7. Tui3 in A-koan koh kong2-tioh8 hiah koan-sim, hiah iau3-kin2, hiah tioh8-kip! Hou7 A-eng sim-thau5 chiok un-loan2. ¡§Goan5-lai5 goa2 to7-si7 ai3 Kheng3-tong5 chit-tiam2.¡¨ A-eng sim-lai7 siuN7. Chit kui2 ni5 lai5, i it-tit8 siuN7 bo5, tau3-te2 i si7 ai3-tioh8 Kheng3-tong5 siaN2? Goan5-lai5 sim-bok8-tiong i3-ai3 e5 ang-sai3, koh-khah tioh8 si7 gin2-a2 e5 ho2 au7-chek. E7 koan-sim, iau3-kin2 gin2-a2 e5 toa7-se3-hang7 tai7-chi3, e7 ui7 gin2-a2 e5 ho2-bai2 lai5 chau2-chong5.... Chit8-peng5 e5 Kheng3-tong5, khoaN3 A-eng long2 bo5 chhut-siaN, ioh si7 soeh-hok8-lek8 bo5-kau3. ¡§Chiah8 tok8 bo5 ho2-boe2, m7-na7 hai7-tioh8 ka-ti7, ma7 thoa-boa5 kui-ke-hoe2.¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 gou7-hoe7 A-eng m7-chai tai7-chi3 e5 khin-tang7, it-tit8 chhian5-ian5, boe7-tang3 tong-ki-lip8-toan7, iu7 koh u7 chhui3 kong2 kah bo5 noa7. Tng teh au3-nau2...., tut8-jian5 thoat-khau2: ¡§Goan2 A-hiong to7-si7 hou7 tok8-phin2 hai7 si2--e5-lah!¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 bo5-i3-tiong thou3 chhut loe7-sim e5 pi3-bit8, beh am-kham3 i2-keng siuN ban7--louh: ¡§....Li2 mai3 koe3-chhui3, ma7 mai3 hou7 Chhai2-giok8 in chai--leh houhN.¡¨
  A-eng khok8-khok8 tim3-thau5, sim-lai7 leh siuN7, ¡§Goan5-lai5 si7 an2-ne, bok8-koai3 i long2 m7-kong2.....¡¨ ¡§Goa2 loh8-khi3 Ko-hiong5 jin7-si si5, khoaN3-tioh8 chhiu2-kou2, toa7-thui2 choan5 chiam-jiah, to7 chai chit8-tiau5 mia7 khi3 hou7 tok8-phin2 be2-siu--khi3. Tok8-phin2 sui-jian5 che7 khoan2, e7 the5-sin5, chheN2 nau2.... Kau3 li2 chiah8 tiau5, oaN7 li2 bo5 ng3 i boe7-tang3 koe3-jit8. SiaN2-mih chhin-chiaN5 peng5-iu2, ang-bou2, bu2-a2-kiaN2 long2 tan3 piN--a2 khi3..., kan-taN ai3 li2 e7-tang3 piaN3 tok8-phin2 hou7 teh gian3. He gian3-thau5 khi2-khi2--khi2-lai5, pi2 siaN2 koh-khah kan-khou2! Ti7 kiau2-tiuN5 to7 bat khoaN3--koe3.... Bai2 to7-si7 goa2 hit-chun7 keng3-kak-seng3 bo5-kau3, kan-taN ioh A-hiong hou7 lang5 khan khi3 sng2, khi3 than3, khi3 poah8, ka7 chhu3-lai7 e5 chiN5 hui2-hui2--tiau7..., bo5 siuN7 kau3 i e7 khi3 hou7 lang5 chhi7 tiau5.... Goa2 hit-chun7 kan-taN e7-hiau2 ka7 me7, ka7 but8...., ia7 boe7-hiau2 ka7 tau3-kha-chhiu2, ...ah bo5, goa2...goa2 ma7 e7 poe5 i khi3 kai2, chong2 kong2 si7 long2 bo5 khi3 siuN7--tioh8....¡¨
  A-eng te7 it pai2 kam2-siu7 tioh8 Kheng3-tong5 kam2-cheng5 e5 liu5-lou7, tang-si5-a2 Kheng3-tong5 ai3 in A-hiong chiah chhim..... ¡§Goa2 hit-chun7 sit-kak-chhah, kan-taN khoaN3 A-hiong chhu3 toa3-boe7-tiau5, saN-kang, nng7-kang oat--leh to7 soan--chhut-khi3, ioh si7 hoan7-chian7 thau chau2 khi3 poah8, khi3 than3, thai3 e7 chai-iaN2 chau2 khi3 teh gian3. Na7 beh chai hit-chun7 tiong3-tok8 iau2 bo5 chhim, pang i kai2 eng3-kai kai2 e7--khi2-lai5......¡¨ A-eng tut8-jian5 chit8-chun7 chit8-chun7 e5 jiu5-cheng5 bit8-i3 lau5 phian3 choan5-sin. Chu7 tit-tioh8 A-hiong koe3-sin liau2-au7, chit8-e5 i3-lian7 put-si5 tiam3 thau5-khak te2 teh seh8, to7-si7 m7-chai beh an2-choaN2 khui-chhui3. Siok8-gi2 kong2 bai2-bai2-a2-ang khah iaN5 bo5, Kheng3-tong5 sui-jian5 chhou-hu, boe7-hiau2 piau2-tat8 kam2-cheng5...., ¡§...Na7 bo5 kin2 chhoa7 tng2-lai5 i, lai5 kai2, A-eng--a, e7 chhiuN7 goa2 sit-khi3 goan2 A-hiong--neh.¡¨ Koan-sim e5 siaN-soeh ma7 u7 iu3-siu3 e5 chit8-bin7, hou7 A-eng chin kam2-sim. ¡§Goa2 long2 thiaN li2 e5 oe7, li2 tioh8-ai3 chhiuN7 lau7-pe7 an2-ne tau3 ka3,¡¨ A-eng chhek oa2 Kheng3-tong5 e5 heng-kham2: ¡§ChhiuN7 goa2 thiaN3 A-nai in an2-ne. Li2 kong2 goa2 u7 chhiuN7 ma-ma an2-ne sioh in--bo5?¡¨ ¡§A-nai in ka-chai3 u7 li2 leh ka3 leh sioh....¡¨ ¡§Li2 chai to7 ho2.....Aih, mai3 kong2 gin2-a2--a-lah.....Li2...li2...u7 ai3 goa2--bo5?¡¨ M7-chai si7 siuN se3-saiN, iah-si7 siaN2 ian5-kou3, Kheng3-tong5 kui-e5-lang5 soah nga7-nga7.
